race.comment: O'CALDINO (4) is a stayer resuming but has revved up for this with a recent trial and is drawn to get a cosy run in transit from gate two. Should be hitting the line with gusto. EAST WEST MISS (11) has been right there in all three outings this preparation and will be ready to peak now fourth-up from the spell. Nicely placed to feature in the finish. BEST COFFEE (1) was a touch disappointing last time out but go on the strong win over this course and distance two back. Worth another chance. INQUISITOR (9) placed around this circuit at the latest effort and hoop Wilson-Taylor sticks in the saddle. Sure to run well again. ROYAL GLADIATOR (10) rounds out the selections in an open race to close out the card.
